{"hca254f06g137eg4d0cgb306gf2f13606b722": ["Do you think we'll stay in Baldur's Gate long?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "4f71e32d-ab89-a52c-27cf-883d6f2460e1"], "h01e2a9b4g3ca4g4ac7gbd49ga3362535670a": ["Of course. It's a big city, lots of opportunity.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "1e76468b-ea17-b9ea-0723-ad87603cf287"], "hf5f7b734g97ceg4453g94d4g588267c3f008": ["But Elturel...", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "94c90c8f-e396-15c9-323d-cc94cc9f4d8e"], "hcfa25b3dgc34cg47b6g93e4g290250a2da22": ["Don't let that place cast a shadow on your head forever.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "6b28f969-33da-315c-4520-3c94b1bd203f"], "hb0d4dd2dg29f4g416egbfccga3ea4ac8b313": ["I guess things are already better. I've learned a lot.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "a86edf5d-b429-c0c3-90d8-a435334d18b1"], "h8d61b1b8gfae5g4d93gabb3gc69620608ed3": ["There we go, boy. Now back to packing.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "c5c6cc43-c35a-638d-5a08-6a03149fd8de"], "hb60343eagd2c4g4eeeg8965g40ecf248ca23": ["What do you think of opening a cart in Baldur's Gate?", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "340564f9-d51e-d812-695d-7dfa27665fb9"], "h41054270g2b70g4de9gb4fbg52e0d1354a52": ["A cart? Like on the street?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "63b3e000-5cf5-cf04-23c1-ec3fb6e56893"], "hdb8f4e20g9993g40c4gbbbdgdd97d94c14aa": ["Exactly. Noble types won't want a tiefling cookin' for them, but common folk...", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "b55e0342-3fd5-c011-b5df-3aff47c2daf5"], "h81b9921ag8445g446bg8fcbg6533d1e2ad09": ["A cart sounds fine, but do I have to haul it around?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "3e0fcb85-4b6f-3ac7-afe0-9d186dfbe379"], "h82ff6974g14f2g45a3g9871g6f4927d221be": ["Until we make the coin for a proper ox, maybe.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "a019c228-2f7c-90f8-d5fd-93171fa262e2"], "h846edbdeg3945g49b1g801dga4714c0857b2": ["*Sigh.*", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "cc832292-1c53-6f3b-7bf3-edf6fb006f4b"], "hf2701130gc617g4652ga7b4g7d88f695eed1": ["Do you need help, Ikaron?", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "fcdec382-a7f9-3c42-9a57-ca16b4e5323f"], "h4371ecdfgcb8dg4ff8g9b52g9db41f83389d": ["Nn-! No. I've got it!", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "d1aa08d1-7e8a-7dbb-bc3f-3818530d4ca2"], "hfb733731g719eg4d0eg9dc2gf9e13d57bced": ["Don't be breaking your back before we get to Baldur's Gate.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "d33a04cc-3b28-c16e-cf91-2951d7b2d998"], "h1cc29af6gada1g41f3ga2e7g8d3c1e9bab0f": ["I won't. I'm not ten any more.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "4e000125-c467-5866-d4fc-d77e416ad5f0"], "h53f826dege6fag4551ga6c1g74a9916a33c0": ["Don't I know it. But there's two more boxes after this one.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "a914883e-81ea-23c1-f0b9-8c124012fcc8"], "hdb40e88eg06f7g4c8dg80b1gf9274298d2cc": ["Ugh.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSonPacking.html", "7d895481-c920-c4ff-9e6b-98f3b8bf4cdd"]}